edsl.commitments

Then

Related Doc: package commitments

case class Then(first: Contract, second: Contract) extends Contract with Product with Serializable

Class for representing a conditional Contract.

first

A Contract object.

second

Another Contract object.

Note

If you acquire Then(first, second) and first contract has not expired, then you acquire the first contract. If the first contract has expired but the second contract has not, then you acquire the second contract. The contract Then(first, second) expires only after both first and second edsl have expired.
